des:
Listen to Sunny 106.7 on your Amazon device(s)!

Sunny 106.7 is your home for Feel Good Music and Feel Good Workdays. 

Once you've enabled the skill, saying "Alexa, OPEN sunny one oh six seven" gets you right in.

Listen to your favorite music from your favorite artists like Taylor Swift, Ed Sheeran, Maroon 5, Adele, and more.
